      "heading": null,
      "description": "Add a drizzle of oil to a wok or frying pan set over a medium-high heat. Once hot, add the onion and garlic and fry for 2-3 mins until starting to soften. Add the coriander stems, chipotle and pineapple, then stir-fry until fragrant. Add the cooked rice, oyster sauce and peppers, then toss until coated."
